items.desc: An awesome and fresh new wiki where you can spend time reading up-to-date pages, submitting your own fan-fictions or rumours in blog posts, role-playing on the forums or chatting with others about the hot new indie game by Scott Cawthon. FNAF World will be played on PC, Android, and iOS.
